ðŸ”¹ Code Blocks
Inline Code
Use backticks for `single commands` like this.

### Multi-line Code Block
Use three backticks (```) followed by the language name (bash, python, html) for syntax highlighting followed by (```) 
example 
```bash
sudo apt update
```

